{"tid":1759032,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"迫政府成立「獨立調查委員會」嘅方法：先和理非，後勇武","createTime":"2019-11-27T11:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T12:07:56.000Z","uid":176951,"like":73,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"02bc3d41ac8505f3da9f4e8b73bad268105f66a0","tid":1759032,"uid":176951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"「勇武」係我哋既大技黎<br />\n話明大技就唔會成日出，唔到生死關頭都唔用，而且手足付出係好大<br />\n<br />\n相反「和理非」係普通技，無乜成本又傷到人，只係效果無大技咁勁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家記唔記得運動開始果陣有條formula:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非 &mdash;&gt; 設下死線&mdash;&gt; 行動升級</span><br />\n<br />\n依家係搬番出黎用既最好時機：<br />\n1.和理非方式唔會迫政府同警隊坐埋同一條船，拉一派打一派<br />\n2. 比普通市民係死線前回氣同有心理準備<br />\n3. 就算到死線政府都唔回應，破壞和諧氣氛既責任就係政府身上，立會選舉贏面又大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：繼續和理非式抗爭一段時間，並設下死線"},{"pid":"f688648dc3e5fb44cb864571b20342ba395c4f01","tid":1759032,"uid":176951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c374a3ba38c1f07dbe71b6d5ec20a788294cc36","tid":1759032,"uid":176951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:00:55.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"2bc71ebf933711bd81845596da0b614df5e06826","tid":1759032,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"0eced3638369e84c525cad28f40b3a535245da5d","tid":1759032,"uid":176951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"4e1f781f5d198c61b9ec2bec48509fbd497c7d85","tid":1759032,"uid":176951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"dec0c3a821479